{"tid":1734814,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪得我一個覺得需要有人係到打Beat?","createTime":"2019-11-18T12:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T12:19:04.000Z","uid":24577,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"efea7449328e37c9b72d3c9cf54943ce0900aa10","tid":1734814,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"正如黑警前進既時候 佢地會打佢地個盾 一路向前 令到手足產生恐懼<br />\n同一時間 可以令到同行既手足知道而家係進係退 唔會一野就比人打散晒<br />\nfor example <br />\n不繼敲打 就係前進既signal <br />\n慢既敲打 就係留守 <br />\n三長兩短既 就係慢慢後退<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法 除左可以令到手足知道而家係共識做咩之餘 聲夠大既話 可以令到對面產生恐懼<br />\n<br />\n大家討論下可唔可行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c454cdc0108648aede2921db438e2f2a2652fa48","tid":1734814,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:03:52.000Z","msg":"執行難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98614494679948150f64cdc53c0e0e23b9427e7c","tid":1734814,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"由前線開始打 二線聽同跟 如果可行 成個形勢唔同好多"},{"pid":"dd8c9158422fc01208bf6c8e1b7ff8e3df01a2a5","tid":1734814,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"真係唔得咩？"},{"pid":"b7f7c50c1f0b3377a50d137c7c6c312ebcc8818d","tid":1734814,"uid":297672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:19:04.000Z","msg":"但問題係，如果有個on9一開頭做錯決定，啲人就會跟住打，咁就好難轉。同埋警察實會知呢啲訊號嘅意思。"}]}